            <title>[LU-14901] consume grants if async write fallback sync io</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14901</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;With OSTSIZE=400000 sanity-quota.sh 10 exposed an intresting problem:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In vvp_io_write_commit() if out of quota, it will try sync write. However in osc_queue_sync_pages(), space grant will be only consumed with DIO.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
